sentences: Oh Ji-Min (born May 27, 1988), known professionally as J-Min, is a South Korean singer, songwriter and musical actress.
J-Min made her debut in Japan with her first extended play, Korogaru Ringo, on September 12, 2007.
On January 16, 2008, J-Min's second Japanese extended play, Dream On... was released.
J-Min released a digital single titled Change/One on May 27, 2009.
The single was her last released under Avex Trax before her contract expired in 2012.
